author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Tile hand safety tips…I had to pull this tile and remove just a fraction of an inch. I’m wearing the Ironclad Command Foam Nitrile gloves. They have Level 2 cut resistance with an extra coating on the fingers & knuckles for added protection. The last thing I need is to hurt my hand and be off the job. Many thanks to Ironclad for sponsoring this video and keeping people safe 🔥#handprotection #ironcladperformancewear #tilework #homerepairtutor #brandpartner
